divs: Sighting Detailsit was canadas day so we had fireworks we were setting the last one off then after it was just about done an object apeared -it was very high in the sky(so it was hard to determine the size) -two lights beside eachother (lights possibly belonged to another craft) -faster than any plane (that we see in our area because our house is a spot where planes fly over) -no sound -we took a couple pictures but the object did not appear at first it looked like a sattelite but it clearly wasen`t the flight path was completely straight my feelings were curiousity to find out what it was the object flew past a tree so we lost our sight
